1.患者女性，68岁，既往高血压病史10年，最高峰值：180/120mmHg,长期服用硝苯地平缓释片1片/次，日3次口服以降压治疗，糖尿病病史20年，诺和灵日1次皮下注射以降糖治疗，脑梗塞病史9年。2.主要特点：头晕，伴有视物旋转，劳累及情绪激动加重，甚则如坐舟船，平卧后好转，口干、口渴，多饮，咽干口苦，时有耳鸣，双下肢水肿，左下肢肢体麻木肿胀疼痛，无发热及畏寒，无肢体及语言活动障碍，无恶心及呕吐，无腹泻等症状。3.查体：T&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt; 35.7℃，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P80&lt;/span&gt;分&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;、R18&lt;/span&gt;次∕分&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;、BP140/70mmHg，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;咽部无充血，两侧扁桃体无肿大，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;口唇无紫绀，颈软无压痛，两肺呼吸动度一致，语颤一致，听诊两肺呼吸音清，两肺听诊未闻及干湿性啰音。左侧巴彬斯基征阳性，其余神经系统检查无阳性体征，余未见异常。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;'&gt;4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0